Chinese medicine after seeing a faith healer after surgery a few years ago. Now 
she offers an acupuncture/massage service and treats people afflicted with 
everything from insomnia to infertility. ; Photo, Loretta Covert Theresa Tamura 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
