Hills." ; Photo, Tim Dunigan starred in short-lived revival of "Davy Crockett." 
; Photo, Harvey Korman and Cloris Leachman in Mel Brooks-produced "Nutt House." 
; Photo, Paul Sorvino, right, in "The Oldest Rookie." 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
