STATES; COMPUTER EQUIPMENT; EQUIPMENT FAILURES; NATIONAL AERONAUTICS AND SPACE 
ADMINISTRATION; RECONNAISSANCE SATELLITES; ASTRONAUTS -- HEALTH; WEATHER 
</P>
