-- PHILIPPINES; UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- PHILIPPINES; UNITED 
STATES -- FOREIGN AID -- PHILIPPINES; MILITARY FORCE REDUCTIONS; UNITED STATES 
-- ARMED FORCES -- PACIFIC RIM NATIONS 
</P>
