<DOCID> 181464 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
February 25, 1990, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Business; Part D; Page 4; Column 3; Financial Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
